reviews.text:
Tips: if you're a local resident, check out a restaurant in this shopping center that offered free meal to those lucky patrons whose last few digits on their ID card match those listed on their promotional poster outside the store front.

I traveled all the way from the Hong Kong island by MTR just to come here to shop.  Features many retail stores, restaurants, travel agencies, and a supermarket just minutes from the MTR Tsuen Station.  Prices are relatively lower than those in the other side of the harbor. Take the C exit which leads all the way to the multistory shopping center.
As i said everything are there. Malls and streets stores
Have to wait for half an hour just waiting for the elevator
Many hot pots options
荃灣鷄煲好味 Enjoy chicken pot here

reviews.text: 可能係荃灣最多食肆的商廈👍👍👍
大型綜合性商場👍
好多不同的美食👍🏼👍🏼👍🏼
荃灣放題店及火鍋店的集中地，在晚餐時間會有大量人群等待乘坐升降機，常把大堂擠得水洩不通。此外大廈的消防安全堪憂，倘若發生火警，情況也許會變得十分混亂。
美食選擇多，可是上落樓層不方便，大堂等升降機的人多。
